data.title: Farquhar Fladhaich (Hothead) VI. Chief Laird of Dumaglass MacGillivray (born Mac Gillavry) (
data.meta_description: Farquhar Fladhaich (Hothead) VI. Chief Laird of Dumaglass MacGillivray (born Mac Gillavry) was born in the year 1655 in Dunmaglass, Inverness, Scotland, United Kingdom, son of Alexander Chief Of Dunmaglass MacGillivray and Agnes Mackintosh., they had 12 children. He died in the year 1714 in Dunmaglass, Inverness-Shire, Schotland. This information is part of M(a)cDonald Family Site - black Jewish YAHYA family line 3 by Dr Wilton McDonald- black Hebrew on Genealogy Online.
